The Glamorous Life of Sachiko Hanai
Basically /b/- The Movie.
[[Image:sachiko.jpg|thumb|box|right|George Bush making an appearance in this movie]]
The Glamorous Life of Sachiko Hanai is a [[Japanese]] porno that makes appearances on [[/b/]] TV because it is so full of [[lulz]]. As well as starring an ugly [[Japanese]] chick with disgustingly large lips, it is full of philospohical and [[stupid|controversial]] ideas. For reasons unknown, [[George Bush]] appears through a bucket of water and Sachiko receives his cloned finger. Guided by a blurry string, it then chases her up a flight of stairs, and fingers her while [[W|George]] sits there and speaks to her in fluent [[Japanese]]. She also gets shot in the head; later on the bullet hole gets fucked, too.

